WEBVTT

00:01:59.807 --> 00:02:03.310
But everything is always a challenge.

00:02:03.673 --> 00:02:07.244
Mostly now, because I think
many of you know

00:02:07.268 --> 00:02:10.124
that the Amazon now is on fire.

00:02:11.186 --> 00:02:13.831
That affects all of us.

00:02:15.371 --> 00:02:19.926
Destroying the Amazon does not affect
just the indigenous people,

00:02:19.950 --> 00:02:22.266
because we are all connected.

00:02:22.578 --> 00:02:25.998
Whatever we do in my community,
if I burn everything,

00:02:26.022 --> 00:02:27.438
it's going to affect it here,

00:02:27.462 --> 00:02:29.839
when the snow comes here at Christmas.

00:02:29.863 --> 00:02:31.276
If you pollute here,